Package: hazprox
Title: Calculate Cumulative Proximity to Hazards for Geographic Areas
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2025-08-25
Authors@R: 
    person("Sarah", "Rockhill", 
            email="srockhill@cdc.gov", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"), 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3197-2825"))
Description: Calculate the cumulative proximity to environmental hazards for
            simple feature polygons. Allows users to calculate average and 
            population-weighted average proximity for a larger areas.
